    "answer_id" : 67337238,
    "question_id" : 21276059,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I have solved this Problem using <code>addBatch</code> and <code>executeBatch</code> as following:</p>\n<pre><code>statement.addBatch(&quot;DELETE FROM public.session_event WHERE id = &quot; + entry.getKey());\nstatement.executeBatch();\n</code></pre>\n"
